Grimes says Elon Musk '/lives/ at times below the poverty line '/and/ would not buy/ a new mattress despite her side having a hole in it
                        ^^^^^                                   ^^^^  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^     
1.劃動詞 連接詞 介系詞 把句子切小段

Grimes says Elon Musk '/lives/ at times below the poverty line'和 would not buy/ a new mattress despite her side having a hole in it
是用and連接的對等的兩個短句 

2.Grimes says Elon Musk '/lives/ at times below the poverty line'的動詞是 lives=>生活在 at times=>有時  
Grimes(Elon Musk的女友)說Elon Musk 有時生活在貧窮線之下

3.would not buy/ a new mattress despite her side having a hole in it(在床墊) 的動詞和介系詞是 would not buy=>不會買 despite=>儘管
      不會買       新床墊        儘管   她的身邊有一個洞

※ 儘管有3種:despite+名詞或動名詞；Although 和 even though 後面要接有「主詞」和「動詞」的完整小句子

4.整句=>Grimes(Elon Musk的女友)說Elon Musk 有時生活在貧窮線之下，儘管她(睡的床墊)身邊有一個洞，Elon Musk不會買新床墊。

Grimes told Vanity Fair that /dating/ Elon Musk, the world's richest person, /made/ her feel "trapped between two worlds."
                              ^^^^^^                                          ^^^^      ^^^^^^^^^^^^^       
                              約會(動名詞放在that後面)                         使          感覺被困

1.遇到逗號先看逗號的句子從屬, the world's richest person, 是Elon Musk的同位語，說明Elon Musk是世界首富.

2.Grimes told Vanity Fair(浮華世界雜誌) that(that代表後面這件事情用子句) /dating/ Elon Musk , the world's richest person 
 Grimes告訴浮華世界雜誌 和世界首富Elon Musk約會

3./made/ her feel "trapped between two worlds.

使她感覺被困在兩個世界之間(她後面就是要解釋是哪兩個世界,應該是富有和貧窮的兩個極端世界吧)

4.整句=>Grimes告訴《浮華世界雜誌》和世界首富Elon Musk約會使她感覺被困在兩個世界之間.

Grimes said her on-again, off-again partner(伴侶)Elon Musk sometimes lived "below the poverty line."

on-again, off-again=>斷斷續續 分分合合

Grimes說和她分分合合的伴侶Elon Musk 生活在貧窮線之下

She said Musk /opted not to buy/ a new mattress /after/ her side /was found to/ have a hole in it.

1.劃動詞 連接詞 介系詞 把句子切小段 after句型,先看after後面的her side /was found to/ have a hole in it(床墊)
                                                                       ^^^^^^^^^^^^
她身邊的床墊被發現有洞      

2.She said Musk /opted not to buy/ a new mattress 
她說Musk選擇不買新床墊

3.她說她身邊的床墊被發現有洞之後Musk選擇不買新床墊

"Bro(Musk) does not live like a billionaire," Grimes told Vanity Fair.
                    ^^^^ 
Musk 不像億萬富翁那樣生活，”Grimes告訴《浮華世界雜誌》.

Grimes said in an interview published this week that her on-again, off-again partner Elon Musk — the world's richest person — sometimes lived "below the poverty line."

— the world's richest person —和, the world's richest person, 用法一樣,代表 Elon Musk的同位語

Grimes在本週發表的一次採訪中說，她分分合合的伴侶世界首富埃隆馬斯克,有時生活在“貧困線以下”。